GamepadButtons.summary:
The Gamepad.buttons property of the {{domxref(&quot;Gamepad&quot;)
}} interface returns an array of objects representing the
buttons present on the device.

remarks.para:
Each entry in the array is 0 if the button is not pressed, and non-zero (typically 1.0)
if the button is pressed. Each object has two properties:
pressed and value:
